Citation.sAbstract: Densities (F) and relative permittivities at five temperatures, between (291.15 and 303.15) K, of binary mixtures of 2-methoxyethanol (1) + dipropylamine (2), are reported. The excess molar volumes and the relative permittivity deviations were calculated from these experimental data. The results are discussed in terms of intermolecular interactions.
Citation.sTitle: Density and Relative Permittivity of 2-Methoxyethanol + Dipropylamine Mixtures at Various Temperatures
